Package org.obrel.type

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutomaticType<T>
    A base class for relation types that update their target or other state automatically based on other relations of the parent object it is set on.
    CollectorType<T>
    An automatic relation type that collects values from other relations of the object it is set on.
    ConstraintType<T>
    A special property relation type that implements constraints on relations.
    CounterType<N extends java.lang.Number>
    An automatic relation type that counts occurrences of other relations.
    ListenerType<L,E>
    A generic event listener relation type.
    ListenerTypes
    Contains standard event listener relation types and event listener type factory methods.
    ListType<T>
    A relation type subclass for List targets that are automatically initialized to an empty list.
    MapType<K,V>
    A relation type subclass for Map targets that are automatically initialized to an empty map.
    MetaTypes
    This class contains definitions of standard meta-relation types.
    SetType<T>
    A relation type subclass for Set targets that are automatically initialized to an empty set.
    StandardTypes
    This class contains definitions of standard relation types.
    TimerType
    A relation type that returns the milliseconds since the creation of a relation with this type.
